(42, 'Import and sale of brand goods Pazzini and Bel. Treatment of damaged,dyed and rusty hair through laser therapy.', 'Pazzini, Bell, Shapin Garay, Laser therapy, Cosmetic means, Hair care products', '.::Laser therapy::.', 'LASER THERAPY', 1435, '<h1>\r\n	LASER THERAPY</h1>\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="2" style="width: 700px; ">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan="2">\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;It is said that beauty requires&nbsp;sacrifice, but&nbsp;it depends on&nbsp;what it is and&nbsp;how much.</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;Having groomed hair every day is a natural desire for every woman, but various hair care means, ecology, external and&nbsp;internal many factors harm our hair seriously, which causes not only aesthetic but also serious functional problems.</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;It is not worth&nbsp;such a&nbsp;risk especially&nbsp;when there is hair care preventative and restorer cosmetic means Allinea.</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;The means of this therapy are designed for&nbsp;any kind of&nbsp;hair and for eliminating different kinds of hair problems.</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp;Allinea is for .</span></p>\r\n				<p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Damaged and dyed hair</span></p>\r\n				<p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Curly hair care</span></p>\r\n				<p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Flattening curly hair</span></p>\r\n				<p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Thin and branched hair</span></p>\r\n				<p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Damaged hair</span></p>\r\n				<p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hair requiring&nbsp;partial flattening</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size: 14px; ">&nbsp; &nbsp;Laser therapy with Allinea is feasible for any type of hair.</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;The materials used in laser therapy are made from absolutely natural raw materials, which include Pappaya,&nbsp;&nbsp;oil of Argan,&nbsp;vitamin E, etc.</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;The materials have passed an appropriate examination of &nbsp;dermatological test. They are anti-allergic and are permissible for pregnant&nbsp;women as well.</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;This therapy can only be applied by highly qualified hairdressers, who understand the structure of hair and who has passed appropriate courses for it.</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;Allinea therapy is a real help for those curly hair women who dream of having straight&nbsp;hair.</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;It is also very effective for keeping curly hair&nbsp;beautiful and lush.</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;Alinea therapy also offers home care.</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;To get maximum&nbsp;protection one must use&nbsp; the liquid called Siroko.</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;You can dress up your hair with a blow dryer or with the help of fingers, that is to say without a comb.</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">And as to dyeing your hair you can do it very quietly on the same day or several days after the therapy.</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align: center; ">\r\n				<a href="views/pictures/terapia/1.-araj-900.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/terapia/1.-araj-320.jpg" /></a></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align: center; ">\r\n				<a href="views/pictures/terapia/1.-heto-900.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/terapia/1.-heto-320.jpg" /></a></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align: center; ">\r\n				&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td style="text-align: center; ">\r\n				&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align: center; ">\r\n				<a href="views/pictures/terapia/4.-araj-900.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/terapia/4.-araj-320.jpg" /></a></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align: center; ">\r\n				<a href="views/pictures/terapia/4.-heto-900.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/terapia/4.-heto-320.jpg" /></a></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align: center; ">\r\n				<a href="views/pictures/terapia/2.-araj-900.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/terapia/2.-araj-320.jpg" /></a></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align: center; ">\r\n				<a href="views/pictures/terapia/2.-heto-900.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/terapia/2.-heto-320.jpg" /></a></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align: center; ">\r\n				<a href="views/pictures/terapia/3.-araj-900.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/terapia/3.-araj-320.jpg" /></a></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align: center; ">\r\n				<a href="views/pictures/terapia/3.-heto-900.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/terapia/3.-heto-320.jpg" /></a></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan="2">\r\n				<h3 align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;"><strong>The Rules of Alinea Therapy</strong></span></h3>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size: 14px; ">1. First, you should wash your hair with number 1 shampoo for 2-3 times, while washing the foam should turn into something like mass of mousse. This will mean that the poras- utikulas of your hair are opened and your hair is cleaned from various harmful cells.</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">2. Next dry you hair with towel to get it just wet, then rub Termaks dividing your hair into sections and brush from top to bottom. Termaks makes your hair elastic, keeps PH balance and makes it easy to work with hair.</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">3. Dry your hair with infrared hairdryer (90%), divide into sections, take 2-3cm thick topknot and rub the substance Elistir (Rigenerante; Intenso; Stile Riccio; Fluid Gel; Hair l-azer) 2sm above the root.</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">4. After rubbing totally divide hair into sections again, take 2-3cm thick topknot, brush it from top to bottom for 4-5 times simultaneously keeping the laser on the direction of the comb. Do the same with your whole hair.</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">5. Leave it quiet for 20 minutes to let the substance infiltrate into hair completely.</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">6. Again divide hair into sections, take 2-3 cm thick hair layer and flatten it with the help of iron (the temperature should be 180-220). The main function of flattening hair with iron is to close hair kutikulas.</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">7. You may dye your hair on the same day or several days after it but if there is no need to color your hair, wash with number 5 shampoo, rub number 3 cream, leave it for 4-5 minutes and then rinse.</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">8. After drying your hair with towel rub the liquid&nbsp; Siero and style your hair just with your hands or a hairdryer.</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">9. Alinea has also home care &hellip; shampoo;&hellip;crem;&hellip;Siera;&hellip;which protect from harmful impacts providing your hair&rsquo;s healthy and beautiful appearance.</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="2" style="width: 700px; ">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align: center; ">\r\n				<a href="views/pictures/terapia/9.-araj-900.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/terapia/9.-araj-220.jpg" /></a></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align: center; ">\r\n				<a href="views/pictures/terapia/9.-mijin-900.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/terapia/9.-mijin-220.jpg" /></a></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align: center; ">\r\n				<a href="views/pictures/terapia/9.-heto-900.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/terapia/9.-heto-220.jpg" /></a></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align: center; ">\r\n				&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td style="text-align: center; ">\r\n				&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td style="text-align: center; ">\r\n				&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align: center; ">\r\n				<a href="views/pictures/terapia/10.-araj-900.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/terapia/10.-araj-220.jpg" /></a></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align: center; ">\r\n				<a href="views/pictures/terapia/10.-mijin-900.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/terapia/10.-mijin-220.jpg" /></a></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align: center; ">\r\n				<a href="views/pictures/terapia/10.-heto-900.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/terapia/10.-heto-220.jpg" /></a></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align: center; ">\r\n				&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td style="text-align: center; ">\r\n				&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td style="text-align: center; ">\r\n				&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align: center; ">\r\n				<a href="views/pictures/terapia/8.-araj-900.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/terapia/8.-araj-220.jpg" /></a></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align: center; ">\r\n				<a href="views/pictures/terapia/8.-mijin-900.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/terapia/8.-mijin-220.jpg" /></a></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align: center; ">\r\n				<a href="views/pictures/terapia/8.-heto-900.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/terapia/8.-heto-220.jpg" /></a></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align: center; ">\r\n				<a href="views/pictures/terapia/7.-araj-900.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/terapia/7.-araj-220.jpg" /></a></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align: center; ">\r\n				<a href="views/pictures/terapia/7.-mijin-900.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/terapia/7.-mijin-220.jpg" /></a></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align: center; ">\r\n				<a href="views/pictures/terapia/7.-heto-900.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/terapia/7.-heto-220.jpg" /></a><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', NULL, '2012-02-03 07:22:42', '2012-04-11 18:55:58', '1', '/terapia', 'eng'),
