(111, 'Պազինի և Բել ապրանքանիշների ապրանքների ներկրում և վաճառք: Վնասված, ներկված և գունաթափված մազերի բուժում լազերային թերապիայի միջոցով:', 'Պազինի, Բել, Շապին Գարայ, Լազերային թերապիա, Կոսմետիկ միջոցներ, Մազի խնամքի միջոցներ', '.::Nails::.', 'Բելլ - 4.1.6', 853, '<h1>\r\n	FRENCH CHIC ART</h1>\r\n<table cellpadding="1" cellspacing="2" style="width: 700px; ">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align: top; ">\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">DECORATING NAIL ENAMEL SET + TEMPLATE FOR PATTERNS</span></p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">Play with trends and find expression in fashion!</span></p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">Become a designer of your manicure! This is a total revolution in French manicure.</span></p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<br />\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">If you want to be trendy, white nail ends are not enough.<br />\r\n					Express yourself,&nbsp; your emotions and design your manicure depending on your mood.<br />\r\n					Every time you can get a diffrent result!<br />\r\n					Your nails can be either elegant or romantic but they are always special because every woman is different.<br />\r\n					Using white matte enamel&nbsp; ART COVER&nbsp; you can get a showy patern.&nbsp;<br />\r\n					Traslucent nail enamel COLOUR FINISH is available&nbsp; in 6 subtle shades (3 with spectacular glitters). It will make your nail look smooth and healthy.<br />\r\n					<br />\r\n					Thanks to long - lasting nail polish formula , the manicure will remain&nbsp; fresh and glossy.&nbsp;<br />\r\n					<br />\r\n					You will be able to change the look of your nails, choosing any of the seven&nbsp; different shapes of patterns in three sizes.<br />\r\n					Step by step instruction:<br />\r\n					Choose the template with your favorite pattern and stick it to the nail.<br />\r\n					Use Art Cover to fill the template with white colour.<br />\r\n					Wait a minute until the white enamel dries and remove the template carefully.<br />\r\n					Use COLOUR FINISH to cover the nails, leave them for thirty seconds to dry and enjoy the new style French manicure!</span></p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align: top; width: 250px; text-align: center; ">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<a href="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.1.nailpolish/4.1.6/big/1.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.1.nailpolish/4.1.6/small/1.jpg" /></a></p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<a href="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.1.nailpolish/4.1.6/big/2.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.1.nailpolish/4.1.6/small/2.jpg" /></a></p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<a href="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.1.nailpolish/4.1.6/big/3.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.1.nailpolish/4.1.6/small/3.jpg" /></a></p>\r\n				<div>\r\n					<a href="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.1.nailpolish/4.1.6/big/4.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.1.nailpolish/4.1.6/small/4.jpg" /></a></div>\r\n				<div>\r\n					&nbsp;</div>\r\n				<div>\r\n					<a href="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.1.nailpolish/4.1.6/big/5.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.1.nailpolish/4.1.6/small/5.jpg" /></a></div>\r\n				<div>\r\n					&nbsp;</div>\r\n				<div>\r\n					&nbsp;</div>\r\n				<div>\r\n					&nbsp;</div>\r\n				<div>\r\n					&nbsp;</div>\r\n				<div>\r\n					&nbsp;</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', NULL, '2012-03-20 01:30:04', '2012-03-29 04:45:59', '0', '/bell-4.1.6', 'arm'),
