ustify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size: 14px; ">Perfect Skin Professional Eye Shadow Base<br />\r\n					<br />\r\n					Used on eyelids before eyeshadow application it enhances its color and prolongs the life of makeup. Prevents showering of the applied eyeshadows and their accumulating in the refractions of the skin on the eyelid.&nbsp;<br />\r\n					Contains mineral UVB filter.<br />\r\n					Application method:<br />\r\n					Spread a small amount of the base gently and evenly all over the eyelid, starting from the lash line. Wait a moment until the base is dry, then do the makeup.</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align: top; width: 250px; text-align: center; ">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<a href="views/pictures/product/bell/3.skin/3.2.faundations/3.2.7/big/1.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/product/bell/3.skin/3.2.faundations/3.2.7/small/1.jpg" /></a></p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<a href="views/pictures/product/bell/3.skin/3.2.faundations/3.2.7/big/2.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/product/bell/3.skin/3.2.faundations/3.2.7/small/2.jpg" /></a></p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<a href="views/pictures/product/bell/3.skin/3.2.faundations/3.2.7/big/3.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/product/bell/3.skin/3.2.faundations/3.2.7/small/3.jpg" /></a></p>\r\n				<div>\r\n					<a href="views/pictures/product/bell/3.skin/3.2.faundations/3.2.7/big/4.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/product/bell/3.skin/3.2.faundations/3.2.7/small/4.jpg" /></a></div>\r\n				<div>\r\n					&nbsp;</div>\r\n				<div>\r\n					<a href="views/pictures/product/bell/3.skin/3.2.faundations/3.2.7/big/5.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/product/bell/3.skin/3.2.faundations/3.2.7/small/5.jpg" /></a></div>\r\n				<div>\r\n					&nbsp;</div>\r\n				<div>\r\n					<a href="views/pictures/product/bell/3.skin/3.2.faundations/3.2.7/big/6.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/product/bell/3.skin/3.2.faundations/3.