(212, 'Импорт и продажа продукции торговово знака Бел и Паззини. Лечение мелированных, поврежденных и окрашенных волос с помощю лазерной терапии.', 'Паззини, Бел, Шапин гарай, Лазерная терапия, Косметические средства, Средство за уходом волосами', '.::Nails::.', 'Белл - 4.1.6', 1986, '<h1>\r\n	FRENCH CHIC ART</h1>\r\n<table cellpadding="1" cellspacing="2" style="width: 700px; ">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align: top; ">\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size: 14px; ">DECORATING NAIL ENAMEL SET + TEMPLATE FOR PATTERNS</span></p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style="font-size: 14px; ">Play with trends and find expression in fashion!</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size: 14px; ">Become a designer of your manicure! This is a total revolution in French manicure.</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<br />\r\n					<span style="font-size: 14px; ">If you want to be trendy, white nail ends are not enough.<br />\r\n					Express yourself,&nbsp; your emotions and design your manicure depending on your mood.<br />\r\n					Every time you can get a diffrent result!<br />\r\n					Your nails can be either elegant or romantic but they are always special because every woman is different.<br />\r\n					Using white matte enamel&nbsp; ART COVER&nbsp; you can get a showy patern.&nbsp;<br />\r\n					Traslucent nail enamel COLOUR FINISH is available&nbsp; in 6 subtle shades (3 with spectacular glitters). It will make your nail look smooth and healthy.<br />\r\n					<br />\r\n					Thanks to long - lasting nail polish formula , the manicure will remain&nbsp; fresh and glossy.&nbsp;<br />\r\n					<br />\r\n					You will be able to change the look of your nails, choosing any of the seven&nbsp; different shapes of patterns in three sizes.<br />\r\n					Step by step instruction:<br />\r\n					Choose the template with your favorite pattern and stick it to the nail.<br />\r\n					Use Art Cover to fill the template with white colour.<br />\r\n					Wait a minute until the white enamel dries and remove the template carefully.<br />\r\n					Use COLOUR FINISH to cover the nails, leave them for thirty seconds to dry and enjoy the new style French manicure!</span></p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align: top; width: 250px; text-align: center; ">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<a href="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.1.nailpolish/4.1.6/big/1.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.1.nailpolish/4.1.6/small/1.jpg" /></a></p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<a href="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.1.nailpolish/4.1.6/big/2.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.1.nailpolish/4.1.6/small/2.jpg" /></a></p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<a href="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.1.nailpolish/4.1.6/big/3.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.1.nailpolish/4.1.6/small/3.jpg" /></a></p>\r\n				<div>\r\n					<a href="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.1.nailpolish/4.1.6/big/4.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.1.nailpolish/4.1.6/small/4.jpg" /></a></div>\r\n				<div>\r\n					&nbsp;</div>\r\n				<div>\r\n					<a href="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.1.nailpolish/4.1.6/big/5.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.1.nailpolish/4.1.6/small/5.jpg" /></a></div>\r\n				<div>\r\n					&nbsp;</div>\r\n				<div>\r\n					&nbsp;</div>\r\n				<div>\r\n					&nbsp;</div>\r\n				<div>\r\n					&nbsp;</div>\r\n				<div>\r\n					&nbsp;</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', NULL, '2012-03-28 03:35:27', '2012-03-29 07:22:03', '0', '/bell-4.1.6', 'rus'),
(213, 'Импорт и продажа продукции торговово знака Бел и Паззини. Лечение мелированных, поврежденных и окрашенных волос с помощю лазерной терапии.', 'Паззини, Бел, Шапин гарай, Лазерная терапия, Косметические средства, Средство за уходом волосами', '.::Nails::.', 'Белл - 4.2.1', 1989, '<h1>\r\n	TOP SHINY</h1>\r\n<table cellpadding="1" cellspacing="2" style="width: 700px; ">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align: top; ">\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size: 14px; ">NAIL PROGRAM LINE &ndash; GLAZER - COLOUR FIXATIVE</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size: 14px; ">It forms very fast drying layer, which gives the nails lasting, intensive shine. It&nbsp; emphasizes the nail polish colour and extends its durability.<br />\r\n					It spreads evenly on the nail and does not contain formaldehyde, toluene or camphor which are harmful for nails.&nbsp; Instructions for use: use as a topcoat after applying a coloured nail polish.&nbsp; After about 60 sec. The nail polish will be perfectly dry and hard.</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align: top; width: 250px; text-align: center; ">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<a href="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.2.nailconditioner/4.2.1/big/1.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.2.nailconditioner/4.2.1/small/1.jpg" /></a></p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n				<div>\r\n					&nbsp;</div>\r\n				<div>\r\n					&nbsp;</div>\r\n				<div>\r\n					&nbsp;</div>\r\n				<div>\r\n					&nbsp;</div>\r\n				<div>\r\n					&nbsp;</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', NULL, '2012-03-28 03:37:00', '2012-03-29 07:22:56', '0', '/bell-4.2.1', 'rus'),
(214, 'Импорт и продажа продукции торговово знака Бел и Паззини. Лечение мелированных, поврежденных и окрашенных волос с помощю лазерной терапии.', 'Паззини, Бел, Шапин гарай, Лазерная терапия, Косметические средства, Средство за уходом волосами', '.::Nails::.', 'Белл - 4.2.2', 1992, '<h1>\r\n	QUICK DRY</h1>\r\n<table cellpadding="1" cellspacing="2" style="width: 700px; ">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align: top; ">\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size: 14px; ">NAIL PROGRAM LINE &ndash; NAIL POLISH DRYING FASTENER</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size: 14px; ">Shortens the time of drying the wet painted nails and makes them shiny. Quick Dry&nbsp; has a quick dry formula&nbsp; - in about 30 seconds&nbsp; the coloured nail polish is perfectly dry and strenthened. It createn a special shiny cover on the nail surface, which protects the nail polish from rubbing off and chipping. Contains UV filters preventing fading and getting yellow in the sun. Shake the bottle before use. Apply on painted nails. The manicure will be ready in 30 seconds.</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align: top; width: 250px; text-align: center; ">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<a href="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.2.nailconditioner/4.2.2/big/1.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.2.nailconditioner/4.2.2/small/1.jpg" /></a></p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', NULL, '2012-03-28 03:38:05', '2012-03-29 07:24:08', '0', '/bell-4.2.2', 'rus'),
(215, 'Импорт и продажа продукции торговово знака Бел и Паззини. Лечение мелированных, поврежденных и окрашенных волос с помощю лазерной терапии.', 'Паззини, Бел, Шапин гарай, Лазерная терапия, Косметические средства, Средство за уходом волосами', '.::Nails::.', 'Белл - 4.2.3', 1995, '<h1>\r\n	FLUO TOP COAT</h1>\r\n<table cellpadding="1" cellspacing="2" style="width: 700px; ">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align: top; ">\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size: 14px; ">NAIL PROGRAM LINE &ndash; UV EFFECT POLISH</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size: 14px; ">Reduces the yellowish shade of the nail plate, glazes, refreshes the colour, gives the nails healthy look.&nbsp; It shines in the ultraviolet, e.g. the sun emits ultraviolet waves, which are detected by the polish.&nbsp; On a sunny day the nails look attractive and healthy with their pale pink shade.</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align: top; width: 250px; text-align: center; ">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<a href="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.2.nailconditioner/4.2.3/big/1.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.2.nailconditioner/4.2.3/small/1.jpg" /></a></p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', NULL, '2012-03-28 03:39:27', '2012-03-29 07:24:24', '0', '/bell-4.2.3', 'rus'),
(216, 'Импорт и продажа продукции торговово знака Бел и Паззини. Лечение мелированных, поврежденных и окрашенных волос с помощю лазерной терапии.', 'Паззини, Бел, Шапин гарай, Лазерная терапия, Косметические средства, Средство за уходом волосами', '.::Nails::.', 'Белл - 4.2.4', 1998, '<h1>\r\n	SO HARD</h1>\r\n<table cellpadding="1" cellspacing="2" style="width: 700px; ">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align: top; ">\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size: 14px; ">NAIL PROGRAM LINE &ndash; NAIL HARDENER</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size: 14px; ">Hypoallergenic preparation hardening the nail plate, protecting against breaking and creaking (apply one coat on clean dry nails). It can be used as top, hardening coat&nbsp; protecting the nail polish and giving it lasting glow ( apply a thin coat on coloured nail polish after drying). It containes keratin, the main element of nails. It does not contain toluen, formaldehyde or camphor.</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align: top; width: 250px; text-align: center; ">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<a href="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.2.nailconditioner/4.2.4/big/1.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.2.nailconditioner/4.2.4/small/1.jpg" /></a></p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', NULL, '2012-03-28 03:56:05', '2012-03-29 07:24:42', '0', '/bell-4.2.4', 'rus'),
(217, 'Импорт и продажа продукции торговово знака Бел и Паззини. Лечение мелированных, поврежденных и окрашенных волос с помощю лазерной терапии.', 'Паззини, Бел, Шапин гарай, Лазерная терапия, Косметические средства, Средство за уходом волосами', '.::Nails::.', 'Белл - 4.2.5', 2001, '<h1>\r\n	NAIL BOOSTER OIL</h1>\r\n<table cellpadding="1" cellspacing="2" style="width: 700px; ">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align: top; ">\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size: 14px; ">NAIL PROGRAM LINE &ndash; CUTICLE OIL</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size: 14px; ">Nail strenthening oil containes wheat oil and apricot stone oil. It moinstens and and conditions<br />\r\n					nails and cuticules around them. Enriched with Panthenol, it protects from harmful effects of the environment. Every evening apply on the nails and surrounding them cuticules. To improve circulation and stimulate growth, massage the oil into the nails. If used before manicure or pedicure, it should be carefully removed with soapy water or nail polish remover, before applying the nail polish, and applied again after drying of nails.</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align: top; width: 250px; text-align: center; ">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<a href="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.2.nailconditioner/4.2.5/big/1.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.2.nailconditioner/4.2.5/small/1.jpg" /></a></p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', NULL, '2012-03-28 03:57:47', '2012-03-30 12:55:57', '0', '/bell-4.2.5', 'rus'),
(218, 'Импорт и продажа продукции торговово знака Бел и Паззини. Лечение мелированных, поврежденных и окрашенных волос с помощю лазерной терапии.', 'Паззини, Бел, Шапин гарай, Лазерная терапия, Косметические средства, Средство за уходом волосами', '.::Nails::.', 'Белл - 4.2.6', 2004, '<h1>\r\n	NAIL CONDITIONER</h1>\r\n<table cellpadding="1" cellspacing="2" style="width: 700px; ">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align: top; ">\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size: 14px; ">NAIL PROGRAM LINE &ndash; NAIL NUTRIENT WITH CERAMIDES.</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size: 14px; ">Hypoallergenic preparation with ceramides strenthens the nail plate. Especially recommended for fragile, brittle nail. Prevents breaking and splitting nails. It covers tiny imperfections of the nail and gives it glow. The preparation&nbsp; does not contain toluen, formaldehyde or camphor so it is absolutely safe for nails leaving them healthy and harder. It can be used instead of transparent nail polish (apply two coats on dry clean nail) or as a base for coloured nail polish which expands its lasting.</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align: top; width: 250px; text-align: center; ">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<a href="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.2.nailconditioner/4.2.6/big/1.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="views/pictures/product/bell/4.nails/4.2.nailconditioner/4.2.6/small/1.jpg" /></a></p>\r\n				<div>\r\n					&nbsp;</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', NULL, '2012-03-28 03:58:53', '2012-03-29 07:25:13', '0', '/bell-4.2.6', 'rus'),
