(330, 'Import and sale of brand goods Pazzini and Bel. Treatment of damaged,dyed and rusty hair through laser therapy.', 'Pazzini, Bell, Shapin Garay, Laser therapy, Cosmetic means, Hair care products', '.::Pazzini::.', 'Hair', 1625, '<p>\r\n	<img alt="" src="views/pictures/product/pazzini/hair-1.jpg" style="text-align: left; " /></p>\r\n<h1 style="text-align: left; ">\r\n	Colored<br />\r\n	Smooth<br />\r\n	Natural</h1>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style="font-size:14px;">Molecula P26, combined with the formula rich in trace elements and vegetal active agents by Biochemical Technology, should be introduced into the dye container bottle. It makes the color 70% brighter and 40% longer lasting.&nbsp;<br />\r\n		Ideal for:</span></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style="font-size:14px;">1. Reawakening shades of color</span></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style="font-size:14px;">2. Preventing color aging</span></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style="font-size:14px;">3. Intensifying results</span></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style="font-size:14px;">4. Fighting color fading</span></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style="font-size:14px;">5. Chemically repairing damaged and dull hair, Restoring body and brightness to the hair.</span></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style="font-size:14px;">Rejuvenates dyed hair for women over 40. Prevents and treats the wearing out of dyed hair. Ensures the safe application of chemical treatments. Reduces the fading of tints, prevents split ends, enhances the effects of chemical treatments protecting the hair structure.</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<table cellpadding="1" cellspacing="2" style="width: 700px; ">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align: top; width: 200px; ">\r\n				<br />\r\n				<img alt="" src="views/pictures/product/pazzini/hair-2.jpg" /></td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<h1>\r\n					Trattamento allineante per capelli</h1>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">Pazzini technology is well-known for innovation and experimentation. This is why the Allynea products formula contains a new molecula, P26, made up of carbocysteine, vegetal proteins and amino acids.&nbsp;<br />\r\n					<br />\r\n					Molecula p26 together with Argan Oil has hair-rebuilding, antioxidant and elasticity-enhancing properties, which deliver immediate and extremely natural results.</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">For maintaining the results of&nbsp;Hair L-Aser Intensificatore&nbsp;treatment at home, recommend the specific products (shampoo, conditioner, serum).</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="width: 200px; ">\r\n				&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align: top; width: 500px; ">\r\n				&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align: top; width: 200px; ">\r\n				<br />\r\n				<img alt="" src="views/pictures/product/pazzini/hair-3.jpg" /></td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align: top; width: 500px; ">\r\n				<h2>\r\n					L-AserTek&nbsp;</h2>\r\n				<p>\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">A revolutionary tool in the world of hair cosmetics. L-aserTek produces a beam of light, which enhances the action of Allynea treatments, improving hair quality as well as the performance of all the treatment components (including dyeing). Shortens operating time and eliminates mechanical actions. Straightens and hardens the keratin in the hair and augments the molecular action of the active ingredients. Our products add to the hair its own natural components, such as Amino Acids, Peptides, Proteins and Enzymes. These components react in the presence of L-AserTek and start off the restructuring process, while strengthening the hair.&nbsp;<br />\r\n					Ideal for:</span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">1.&nbsp;Necessary for all Pazzini treatments (intensifies the effect of Elisir by 25%, eliminates mechanical 